<p><strong>Persuasion Scenarios</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>Recruiting a person into your mission</li>
  <li>Getting an investor to back your team</li>
  <li>Forging alliances</li>
  <li>Convincing a customer to try your product</li>
</ul>

